---
import Layout from "../layouts/index.astro";
import ModeToggle from "../components/mode-toggle";
---

<Layout>
  <div
    class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert prose-p:indent-4 prose-p:text-base sm:prose-p:text-lg md:prose-p:text-xl lg:prose-p:text-2xl xl:prose-p:text-3xl mx-auto my-6 w-full max-w-prose px-6 text-justify font-extralight text-balance hyphens-manual sm:max-w-2xl sm:px-8 md:my-8 md:max-w-3xl lg:my-20 lg:max-w-4xl lg:px-6 xl:my-16 xl:max-w-6xl xl:px-4"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 tracking-[0.2em]">
      <h1
        class="text-left text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
      >
        Meet me, Yusoof Moh
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mt-1 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-1 tracking-[0.2em] sm:my-2 sm:gap-2 md:my-3 md:gap-3 lg:my-4 lg:gap-4 xl:my-5 xl:gap-5"
    >
      <ModeToggle client:load />
    </div>
    <div data-mode="detail" class="space-y-4">
      <p>
        In the name of Allah, and by His grace. My name is pronounced <i
          >yu-soof</i
        >. Born and raised in Malang, now collaborating remotely across
        Indonesia. I am a
        <strong>full-stack engineer</strong> building reliable products for SMEs.
        <strong>Web:</strong> TypeScript/React (TanStack), Node/Bun, Hono;
        <strong>DevOps:</strong> Docker, Traefik, CI/CD;
        <strong>Mobile:</strong> React Native/Capacitor;
        <strong>Observability:</strong> Sentry, SigNoz. Recently, I have been standardizing
        CI/CD across monorepos and shipping a
        <strong>multi-tenant booking &amp; operations platform</strong> (web + mobile)
        end-to-end&mdash;from schema and APIs to Docker Swarm deployments and dashboards.
        Beyond code, I cultivate edamame, enjoy regional motorcycle tours, and keep
        a steady habit of deep research. I base my understanding of Islam in accordance
        with the first three generations of the ummah, focusing on <strong
          >tawhid</strong
        >
        and <strong>tafsir</strong>. To further that commitment, I conduct
        private
        <i>tahsin</i> classes and support local Muslim communities, aspiring to contribute&mdash;however
        small&mdash;to the da'wah.
        <span class="font-semibold"
          >Open to meaningful remote/contract collaborations.</span
        >
        You can reach out via
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="mailto:me@yusoofsh.id"
          onclick="sa_event('email_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Mail</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/twitter"
          onclick="sa_event('twitter_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Twitter</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/linkedin"
          onclick="sa_event('linkedin_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">LinkedIn</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/github"
          onclick="sa_event('github_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">GitHub</a
        >. May Allah bless our endeavors, and lead us to His everlasting mercy.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div data-mode="tldr" class="space-y-4">
      <p>
        Bismillah. I'm a Malang-based, remote
        <strong>full-stack engineer</strong> for SMEs delivering end-to-end
        <strong>TypeScript/React (TanStack)</strong>, Node/Bun, Hono systems
        with Docker, Traefik, CI/CD, React Native/Capacitor mobile, and
        observability via Sentry/SigNoz, currently shipping a
        <strong>multi-tenant booking &amp; operations platform</strong> while pursuing
        deep research, edamame cultivation, regional motorcycle tours, and Islamic
        learning centered on <strong>tawhid</strong> and <strong>tafsir</strong>
        through private <i>tahsin</i> classes, open to meaningful
        <strong>remote/contract collaborations</strong> via
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="mailto:me@yusoofsh.id"
          onclick="sa_event('email_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Mail</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/twitter"
          onclick="sa_event('twitter_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">Twitter</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/linkedin"
          onclick="sa_event('linkedin_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">LinkedIn</a
        > /
        <a
          class="not-prose cursor-pointer font-semibold hover:underline"
          href="/github"
          onclick="sa_event('github_clicked')"
          rel="noreferrer"
          target="_blank">GitHub</a
        >. Baarakallahu fiik.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
